  "texts": [
    "In the \"Arithmetic\" test, the PIL-enhanced Mistral demonstrated improved accuracy in performing basic mathematical operations.",
    "This improvement indicates a more effective handling of numerical information and an enhanced ability to apply mathematical logic in language processing tasks.",
    "Finally, the \"Boolean Expressions\" test, which evaluates the model's skill in processing logical expressions, saw considerable gains with the PIL integration.",
    "This emphasizes the PIL's role in enhancing the model's computational logic skills, a crucial factor in various information processing scenarios.",
    "Overall, these results showcase the PIL's effectiveness in elevating the Mistral LLM's factual information retrieval capabilities."
  ]
}